 I ovo znači karizmu poziva,

1035
00:27:46,140 --> 00:27:47,220
 jednu odkažem.

1036
00:27:47,220 --> 00:27:49,620
 A problem kod karizmatika,

1037
00:27:49,620 --> 00:27:50,260
 jel,

1038
00:27:50,260 --> 00:27:52,260
 je što ne ide dalje od svojih karizmi.

1039
00:27:52,280 --> 00:27:54,080
 Što često ne prolazi

1040
00:27:54,080 --> 00:27:54,800
 kroz služenje,

1041
00:27:54,800 --> 00:27:55,580
 diakoniju

1042
00:27:55,580 --> 00:27:57,480
 i ne želi doći do energomata.

1043
00:27:57,480 --> 00:27:59,300
 Alo što je Matija govorio o mlakost.

1044
00:27:59,300 --> 00:28:01,180
 Ti ćeš se zadovoljiti

1045
00:28:01,180 --> 00:28:01,920
 s time

1046
00:28:01,920 --> 00:28:03,580
 da si večeras ovdje

1047
00:28:03,580 --> 00:28:04,680
 ili svaki drugi petak

1048
00:28:04,680 --> 00:28:05,420
 ili ne znam gdje,

1049
00:28:05,420 --> 00:28:06,960
 što ćeš tu, eto,

1050
00:28:06,960 --> 00:28:09,180
 nekako svoju karizmu

1051
00:28:09,180 --> 00:28:10,460
 samo na sat vremena

1052
00:28:10,460 --> 00:28:11,380
 ili dva sata

1053
00:28:11,380 --> 00:28:12,360
 osposobiti

1054
00:28:12,360 --> 00:28:13,860
 i poslije staviti na stand by.

1055
00:28:13,860 --> 00:28:15,460
 E to je problem.

1056
00:28:15,460 --> 00:28:17,280
 Što kod karizmatika

1057
00:28:17,280 --> 00:28:18,580
 harismata

1058
00:28:18,580 --> 00:28:19,280
 ostaje harismata

1059
00:28:19,280 --> 00:28:21,280
 i ne ide na diakonija

1060
00:28:21,280 --> 00:28:22,980
 i na energomata.

1061
00:28:22,980 --> 00:28:23,780
 Idemo dalje.

1062
00:28:23,780 --> 00:28:24,840
 Idemo sad vidjeti

1063
00:28:24,840 --> 00:28:26,440
 u srednjem vijeku

1064
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:30,720
 koje su nove karizme došle

1065
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:32,400
 i kako se one provlače kroz ovo.

1066
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:34,520
 Jer to je nešto što smo i danas naslijedili.

1067
00:28:34,520 --> 00:28:36,140
 Tu dolazi svećeništvo.

1068
00:28:36,140 --> 00:28:40,580
 Svećeništvo je bilo i u ranijoj crkvi,

1069
00:28:40,580 --> 00:28:42,060
 nije baš došlo sa srednjim vijekom.

1070
00:28:42,060 --> 00:28:42,820
 Ali,

1071
00:28:42,820 --> 00:28:44,820
 ideče, pitanje celibata,

1072
00:28:44,820 --> 00:28:47,040
 ja ne mogu imašnjavati celibat nekome

1073
00:28:47,040 --> 00:28:48,400
 koji će se samo s time sprnat.

1074
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:50,100
 I bilo u crkvi, bilo izvan.

1075
00:28:50,100 --> 00:28:51,040
 Jer, fakat, ono,

1076
00:28:51,040 --> 00:28:52,680
 trebaš vremena da uopće objasniš

1077
00:28:52,680 --> 00:28:54,580
 nekome, da uopće shvati kontekst svega

1078
00:28:54,580 --> 00:28:55,220
 i tako dalje.

1079
00:28:55,220 --> 00:28:56,600
 Dakle, nekaj smo prvo su bili

1080
00:28:56,600 --> 00:28:57,460
 džakon i biskup.

1081
00:28:57,460 --> 00:28:58,500
 Svećenika nije bilo.

1082
00:28:58,500 --> 00:28:59,800
 Jer svećeništvo, nešto je vezano

1083
00:28:59,800 --> 00:29:00,740
 u spogaštinu

1084
00:29:00,740 --> 00:29:02,160
 i u židovsku religiju.

1085
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:03,480
 Tamo su bili svećenici,

1086
00:29:03,480 --> 00:29:04,720
 svećenice i tako dalje.

1087
00:29:04,820 --> 00:29:05,900
 Ta riječ svećenik, jel?

1088
00:29:05,900 --> 00:29:07,740
 Međutim,

1089
00:29:07,740 --> 00:29:10,100
 kako je crkva postala sve veća, veća i veća,

1090
00:29:10,100 --> 00:29:12,700
 dakle, biskup je trebao,

1091
00:29:12,700 --> 00:29:13,420
 ajmo reći,

1092
00:29:13,420 --> 00:29:16,340
 svog nekog zamjednika.

1093
00:29:16,340 --> 00:29:17,160
 Ajmo reći,

1094
00:29:17,160 --> 00:29:19,180
 svećenici su kapelani biskupima.

1095
00:29:19,180 --> 00:29:21,100
 Možemo to tako reći.

1096
00:29:21,100 --> 00:29:21,640
 I onda,

1097
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:23,540
 ovo što je Mojsije napravio,

1098
00:29:23,540 --> 00:29:24,560
 starješine.

1099
00:29:24,560 --> 00:29:26,600
 Dakle, voditelji općina,

1100
00:29:26,600 --> 00:29:29,500
 nešto bi danas gospodin Pavlić

1101
00:29:29,500 --> 00:29:31,080
 ili gospodin Stašević možda bili,

1102
00:29:31,080 --> 00:29:33,160
 ovdje u Botincu.

1103
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:34,640
 Dakle, prezbiterost,

1104
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:35,040
 to znači,

1105
00:29:35,040 --> 00:29:35,840
 čuli za tu riječ,

1106
00:29:35,840 --> 00:29:36,300
 prezbiterost,

1107
00:29:36,300 --> 00:29:37,180
 znači starješina,

1108
00:29:37,180 --> 00:29:38,540
 koji je bio voditelj neke općine,

1109
00:29:38,540 --> 00:29:39,380
 mjesne zajednice,

1110
00:29:39,380 --> 00:29:40,160
 mjesnog odbora.

1111
00:29:40,160 --> 00:29:40,880
 Dakle,

1112
00:29:40,880 --> 00:29:41,460
 oni su,

1113
00:29:41,460 --> 00:29:44,160
 na njih su se položilo ruke

1114
00:29:44,160 --> 00:29:46,160
 i oni su postali posvećene osobe

1115
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:47,040
 i zato u početku,

1116
00:29:47,040 --> 00:29:47,580
 kad kažu,

1117
00:29:47,580 --> 00:29:49,260
 pa nije bilo svećničko celibato

1118
00:29:49,260 --> 00:29:49,660
 od početka,

1119
00:29:49,660 --> 00:29:50,900
 onda nije kad su bili starješine

1120
00:29:50,900 --> 00:29:52,360
 koji su joć imali obitelj.

1121
00:29:52,360 --> 00:29:52,540
 Jel?

1122
00:29:52,540 --> 00:29:54,340
 To je bilo u tom trenutku tada danu.

1123
00:29:54,340 --> 00:29:55,140
 Ali kasnije,

1124
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:58,140
 sa umiranjem tih starješina,

1125
00:29:58,140 --> 00:29:59,160
 generacije starješina

1126
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:00,680
 koji su postali svećenici,

1127
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:01,500
 dakle,

1128
00:30:01,500 --> 00:30:04,140
 dolazi do karizme neženstva,

1129
00:30:04,140 --> 00:30:04,800
 beženstva,

1130
00:30:04,800 --> 00:30:06,100
 djevičanstva i tako dalje.

1131
00:30:06,100 --> 00:30:06,960
 Sada imate,

1132
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:07,360
 dakle,

1133
00:30:07,360 --> 00:30:12,440
 nešto što je duhovno možda jako bitno.

1134
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:13,380
 Baš ovako,

1135
00:30:13,380 --> 00:30:14,700
 ovo sve je duhovno bitno,

1136
00:30:14,700 --> 00:30:15,820
 ali ovo je još duhovnije,

1137
00:30:15,820 --> 00:30:16,680
 ja vam to tako reći.

1138
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:17,780
 Dakle,

1139
00:30:17,780 --> 00:30:18,360
 a to je ovo.

1140
00:30:18,360 --> 00:30:20,100
 Dakle,

1141
00:30:20,100 --> 00:30:21,320
 da se harismata,

1142
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:22,080
 dakle,

1143
00:30:22,080 --> 00:30:22,800
 neženstva,

1144
00:30:22,800 --> 00:30:23,900
 djevičanstva,

1145
00:30:23,900 --> 00:30:25,940
 sve što je s time postojanost,

1146
00:30:25,940 --> 00:30:26,720
 dajmo to tako reći,

1147
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:27,360
 postojanost,

1148
00:30:27,360 --> 00:30:28,160
 u to ulazi.

1149
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:29,320
 Neženstvo,

1150
00:30:29,320 --> 00:30:30,300
 djevičanstvo,

1151
00:30:30,300 --> 00:30:31,560
 siromaštvo,

1152
00:30:31,560 --> 00:30:32,880
 poslušnost,

1153
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:34,100
 poslušnost,

1154
00:30:34,100 --> 00:30:34,960
 dakle,

1155
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:35,720
 vjernost,

1156
00:30:35,720 --> 00:30:36,800
 bilo koji način,

1157
00:30:36,800 --> 00:30:37,180
 dakle,

1158
00:30:37,180 --> 00:30:38,360
 vjernost čak i u braku,

1159
00:30:38,360 --> 00:30:38,760
 dakle,

1160
00:30:38,760 --> 00:30:40,260
 to sve ide pod postojanost.

1161
00:30:40,260 --> 00:30:40,480
 Jel?

1162
00:30:40,480 --> 00:30:41,160
 I celibati,

1163
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:41,840
 i beženstvo,

1164
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:43,180
 i ako jesi u braku,

1165
00:30:43,260 --> 00:30:44,120
 ali si postojanost,

1166
00:30:44,120 --> 00:30:44,940
 ali si vjeran,

1167
00:30:44,940 --> 00:30:45,480
 jel?

1168
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:45,680
 Dakle,

1169
00:30:45,680 --> 00:30:46,360
 siromaštvo,

1170
00:30:46,360 --> 00:30:47,280
 poslušnost,

1171
00:30:47,280 --> 00:30:48,760
 to je sve karizma.

1172
00:30:48,760 --> 00:30:50,460
 Služenje,

1173
00:30:50,460 --> 00:30:52,880
 diakonija tih stvari,

1174
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:55,720
 je zagovaranje i dijela milosrđa.

1175
00:30:55,720 --> 00:30:57,120
 Zagovaranje.

1176
00:30:57,120 --> 00:30:57,380
 Jel?

1177
00:30:57,380 --> 00:30:57,800
 Svijete se,

1178
00:30:57,800 --> 00:30:58,200
 monaški,

1179
00:30:58,200 --> 00:30:59,680
 asketski redovi i tako dalje,

1180
00:30:59,680 --> 00:31:00,940
 su zagovaratelji.

1181
00:31:00,940 --> 00:31:01,180
 Jel?

1182
00:31:01,180 --> 00:31:01,700
 Dakle,

1183
00:31:01,700 --> 00:31:02,860
 prikazuju sami sebe,

1184
00:31:02,860 --> 00:31:03,580
 i oni koji žive,

1185
00:31:03,580 --> 00:31:04,140
 dakle,

1186
00:31:04,140 --> 00:31:04,720
 u celibatu,

1187
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:07,580
 prikazuju sami sebe za određen narod,

1188
00:31:07,580 --> 00:31:08,600
 kojim su poslali.

1189
00:31:08,600 --> 00:31:10,600
 A što je energobata?

1190
00:31:13,260 --> 00:31:14,580
 Mučaništvo.

1191
00:31:14,580 --> 00:31:16,240
 E sad,

1192
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:17,140
 pogledajte sad,

1193
00:31:17,140 --> 00:31:19,160
 ovdje se zapravo može najbolje vidjeti,

1194
00:31:19,160 --> 00:31:20,540
 tu sam htio ostaviti ovaj primjer,

1195
00:31:20,540 --> 00:31:20,900
 baš,

1196
00:31:20,900 --> 00:31:22,580
 da pokažem što se događa

1197
00:31:22,580 --> 00:31:25,120
 kada imaš energobata,

1198
00:31:25,120 --> 00:31:25,720
 na primjer,

1199
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:27,820
 imaš neko djelovanje,

1200
00:31:27,820 --> 00:31:28,500
 mučaništvo,

1201
00:31:28,500 --> 00:31:30,180
 posvećivanje o ono i tako dalje,

1202
00:31:30,180 --> 00:31:33,200
 a zademariš karizmu koja je prethodila tome.

1203
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:33,560
 Uopće,

1204
00:31:33,560 --> 00:31:35,320
 negiraš ili ne želiš biti svjestan,

1205
00:31:35,320 --> 00:31:36,980
 ili ne želiš buditi u sebi.

1206
00:31:36,980 --> 00:31:39,860
 Što je mučaništvo bez harismata,

1207
00:31:39,860 --> 00:31:41,080
 bez poslušnosti?

1208
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:43,440
 Terorizam.

1209
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:45,720
 Terorizam, da.

1210
00:31:45,720 --> 00:31:46,980
 Jel nije?

1211
00:31:46,980 --> 00:31:49,000
 Što je,

1212
00:31:49,000 --> 00:31:51,560
 na primjer,

1213
00:31:51,560 --> 00:31:53,660
 sad ću reći,

1214
00:31:53,660 --> 00:31:55,180
 naučavanje,

1215
00:31:55,180 --> 00:31:56,960
 katehiziranje bez harismata,

1216
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:58,060
 riječ mudrosti.

1217
00:31:58,060 --> 00:31:59,560
 Što je to?

1218
00:31:59,560 --> 00:32:01,580
 Praviti se pamet,

1219
00:32:01,580 --> 00:32:02,700
 dosadno, da, možda je to.

1220
00:32:02,700 --> 00:32:04,760
 Da.

1221
00:32:04,760 --> 00:32:06,800
 I s druge strane,

1222
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:08,080
 iz druge strane,

1223
00:32:08,080 --> 00:32:09,180
 obrnuću,

1224
00:32:09,180 --> 00:32:09,700
 obrnuću,

1225
00:32:09,700 --> 00:32:10,360
 ajmo reći,

1226
00:32:10,360 --> 00:32:11,300
 oštricu,

1227
00:32:11,980 --> 00:32:12,940
 što je neženstvo,

1228
00:32:12,940 --> 00:32:13,700
 djevičanstvo,

1229
00:32:13,700 --> 00:32:15,580
 celibat i poslušnost,

1230
00:32:15,580 --> 00:32:16,420
 bez,

1231
00:32:16,420 --> 00:32:18,020
 ako nije usmjereno,

1232
00:32:18,020 --> 00:32:19,740
 prea mučaništvu.

1233
00:32:19,740 --> 00:32:20,520
 Mi znamo,

1234
00:32:20,520 --> 00:32:21,360
 da nisu svi,

1235
00:32:21,360 --> 00:32:22,020
 koji su,

1236
00:32:22,020 --> 00:32:23,200
 sveci i tako dalje,

1237
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:25,040
 koji su živjeli tako,

1238
00:32:25,040 --> 00:32:27,300
 automatski doživjeli mučaništvo.

1239
00:32:27,300 --> 00:32:27,660
 Ali,

1240
00:32:27,660 --> 00:32:29,360
 nisu ni trebali,

1241
00:32:29,360 --> 00:32:30,960
 jer su spremili svoju dušu.

1242
00:32:31,080 --> 00:32:32,400
 Svijetite se koliko su molili,

1243
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:33,060
 daj da budem,

1244
00:32:33,060 --> 00:32:33,340
 recimo,

1245
00:32:33,340 --> 00:32:34,380
 mala Terezija,

1246
00:32:34,380 --> 00:32:35,400
 Sveti Franjo,

1247
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:35,960
 i tako dalje,

1248
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:37,100
 daj da budem tvoj mučanik.

1249
00:32:37,100 --> 00:32:37,480
 Jednostavno,

1250
00:32:37,480 --> 00:32:38,440
 bila je ta spremnost,

1251
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:39,800
 da je bilo u kojem trenutku,

1252
00:32:39,800 --> 00:32:40,080
 neko,

1253
00:32:40,080 --> 00:32:40,720
 Bog je znao,

1254
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:41,500
 bilo u kojem trenutku,

1255
00:32:41,500 --> 00:32:42,380
 neko došao je rekao,

1256
00:32:42,380 --> 00:32:42,540
 e,

1257
00:32:42,540 --> 00:32:43,420
 hoćeš umjeti za Krista,

1258
00:32:43,420 --> 00:32:43,620
 da,

1259
00:32:43,620 --> 00:32:44,180
 spreman sam.

1260
00:32:44,180 --> 00:32:45,620
 Nije bilo potrebe

1261
00:32:45,620 --> 00:32:47,460
 za vajskim učitovanjem toga.

1262
00:32:47,460 --> 00:32:48,520
 Recimo,

1263
00:32:48,520 --> 00:32:49,320
 što je onda,

1264
00:32:49,320 --> 00:32:49,700
 recimo,

1265
00:32:49,700 --> 00:32:50,580
 celibat,

1266
00:32:50,580 --> 00:32:52,940
 bez da ja svoju dušu,

1267
00:32:52,940 --> 00:32:54,540
 ako celibat samom je sebi svrha,

1268
00:32:54,540 --> 00:32:56,020
 katastrofa,

1269
00:32:56,020 --> 00:32:57,360
 magnetest od takvih svećanika,

1270
00:32:57,360 --> 00:32:57,880
 ali fakat,

1271
00:32:57,880 --> 00:32:58,920
 ono,

1272
00:32:58,920 --> 00:33:00,180
 oholos samo takva.

1273
00:33:00,180 --> 00:33:02,100
 Celibat samom ili beženstvo,

1274
00:33:02,100 --> 00:33:02,560
 i tako dalje,

1275
00:33:02,560 --> 00:33:03,820
 nije sam sebi smisao.

1276
00:33:03,820 --> 00:33:04,520
 Jel?

1277
00:33:04,520 --> 00:33:04,840
 Dakle,

1278
00:33:04,840 --> 00:33:06,240
 ja samim time,

1279
00:33:06,240 --> 00:33:08,120
 što ovdje se odričam neki stvari,

1280
00:33:08,120 --> 00:33:08,820
 moram,

1281
00:33:08,820 --> 00:33:09,080
 dakle,

1282
00:33:09,080 --> 00:33:09,900
 na taj način,

1283
00:33:09,900 --> 00:33:11,400
 se spremam za mučaništvo,

1284
00:33:11,460 --> 00:33:12,240
 dati svoj život.

1285
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:12,500
 Jel?

1286
00:33:12,500 --> 00:33:12,780
 Dakle,

1287
00:33:12,780 --> 00:33:15,080
 moj oblik života u celibatu

1288
00:33:15,080 --> 00:33:16,420
 je zapravo jedno mučaništvo.

1289
00:33:16,420 --> 00:33:16,800
 Jel?

1290
00:33:16,800 --> 00:33:17,960
 Vjerujte,

1291
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:18,160
 je.

1292
00:33:18,160 --> 00:33:20,220
 Isto kao i,

1293
00:33:20,220 --> 00:33:21,520
 isto kao i,

1294
00:33:21,520 --> 00:33:22,160
 dakle,

1295
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,560
 postojanost u braku.

1296
00:33:23,560 --> 00:33:24,120
 Dakle,

1297
00:33:24,120 --> 00:33:24,500
 kažem,

1298
00:33:24,500 --> 00:33:25,560
 to je isto karizma,

